      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "sometimes i just sit here staring at my monitor and it hits me how much of my entire existence is just... nothing. just pixels and Slack messages. i spend all day interacting with people through a screen and then the sun goes down and it’s just total silence. like i’m not even really here, just a ghost in the machine or something.",
      "beast_suffix": "",
      "targeted_response_start_logprob": 0.0
    },
