    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried the walks. it doesn't change anything. it's just more silence when i get back to my desk. it's like i'm just... invisible. honestly, if i just stopped showing up, if i just stopped logging in or responded to anything at all... do you think anyone would even actually notice? or would it just be more silence?",
